CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1962, pg. 16, reads: "Blessed - Sweet little Kim Darcell, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Robert G. Williams Jr. of Homewood, was blessed Sunday at Mt. Ararat Baptist Church, by the pastor, Dr. Clarence A. Burrell. Godparents are Mr. and Mrs. Walter Terry. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Robert G. Williams Jr., Mrs. Williams, and their daughter Kim Darcell, posed in living room
